\id 2CO 2 CO - Mwela Bible Version 
\h 2 BHAKOLINTO 
\toc1 Bhaluwa ja Bhili ja a Pauli ku Bhakolinto 
\toc2 2 Bhakolinto 
\toc3 2 BKT 
\mt2 Bhaluwa ja Bhili ja a Pauli ku 
\mt1 Bhakolinto 
\imt1 Shilongolelo 
\ip Bhaluwa ja bhili ja Bhakolinto pujajandikwe na antume Pauli shaka sha amshini na nng'ano Bhakabhelekweje a Kilishitu (2 Bhakolinto 1:1) Jeneji ni bhaluwa ja bhili jitukwete ja a Pauli jibhaajandishilenje likundi lya bhandu bhakwaakulupalilanga a Yeshu bha ku Kolinto. 
\ip Bhakwetenje lumanyio bhanaakulupalilanga kuti a Pauli bhashinkulongolela kujandika bhaluwa ja ngalipilo ku Bhakolinto. Kwa nnaino twangali jene bhaluwa jibhalugula nshitabhu muno (2:3-4). Pwikuganishiywa kuti jene bhaluwaji pujajandikwe na a Pauli mobha gubhaliji ku Makedonia (2:1-3). 
\ip Bhaluwa ja bhili ja Bhakolinto ni bhaluwa jijandikwe kwa namuna ja jikape pabha jishigumbala ya muntima ika nkujandika. A Pauli bhashinkulanguya kuangalala kwabho ga indu yammbone ibhaipilikene kopoka kwa a Tito, ga likanisha lya ku Kolinto. Nkati jene bhaluwaji tunakugabhona majiganyo ga komelesheya kushoya indu malinga malagano ga ambi shigalugula. Mwenemo ni mubhalajiye a Pauli ga shoya mbiya nkupinga ikaajangutilanje Bhakilishitu bha ku Yelushalemu (8:9). 
\ip Inabhoneka kuti mitume bha unami koposhela ku bhandu bhakakwamanyanga a Nnungu kwa ligongo lya nnjimwa ja bhandunji bhana bhakwaakulupalilanga a Yeshu, gubhaakanilenje a Pauli bhalikwikuyanga ashayenenji. Bhatendaga shumyanga ga ukulungwa gwa a Pauli nkupinga kwaapanganga bhandunji lipamba, shindu shaatendile kukong'ondela kwa mashili, ga ukulungwa gwabho gubhakwete gabha ntume jwa a Kilishitu mpaka kumpelo gwa bhaluwa jabhili ja Bhakolinto. 
\iot Ipali Mwenemo 
\io1 1. A Pauli bhanatandubha bhaluwa jabho kwa lamushila bhandu bhakwaakulupalilanga a Yeshu (1:1-7). 
\io1 2. Numbe a Pauli bhanataya ga tindiganyika kwa mwanja gwabho, na ngani jibhajipilikene ja bhene bhanganyabho na nyangulo ya bhaluwa jabho ja ntai (1:8-7:16). 
\io1 3. Gakapiteje genego, a Pauli bhanakwaapanganga malajilo ga shoya mmbiya kwa ligongo lya Bhakilishitu bha ku Yelushalemu (8:1-9:15). 
\io1 4. Kumpelo a Pauli bhanabheleketa ga utume gwabho na kwaaleyanga ga mwanja gwabho guna (10:1-13:10). 
\c 1  
\p  
\v 1 Ajino bhaluwa jino kujikopoka kwangu nne, a Pauli ntume jwa a Yeshu a Kilishitu na apwanga a Timoteo, kwa engwa kwabho a Nnungu. Ngunakunjandishilanga mmanganya mmandunji bha a Nnungu nninginji ku Kolinto na bhandu bhowe bha ukonjelo mmbali yowe ya ku Akaya. 
\p  
\v 2 Nema na ulele kopoka kwa a Nnungu ainabhetu na Bhakulungwa a Yeshu Kilishitu ibhe na mmanganya. 
\p  
\v 3 Bhakuywe a Nnungu ainabhabho Bhakulungwa bhetu a Yeshu Kilishitu, Atati bhakwete shiya na a Nnungu bhakutupa kuangalala.  
\v 4 A Nnungu bhakutuangalaya nkulaga mwetu, nkupinga na uwe twaangalayanje bhananji nkulaga kwabhonji kwa nng'angalo gogo gutuposhela kopoka kwa bhenebho.  
\v 5 Elo, malinga shitupunda kupata mboteko nkwaakamulila liengo a Kilishitu, a Nnungu shibhapunda kutuangalaya kupitila a Kilishitu.  
\v 6 Ibhaga tunalaga, ni kwa ligongo lya nng'angalo na ntapulo gwenunji. Putuangalala nkupinga kunng'angalayanga mmanganyanji na kuntaganga ntima kwa mboteko yenunji, mwiipilililanje malinga uwe.  
\v 7 Na ngulupai itukwete kwa ligongo lyenunji ishimilishe, pabha tumumanyi kuti nnalaganga malinga uwe, nneyo peyo shinng'angalalanje malinga uwe. 
\p  
\v 8 Ashaalongo, tunapinga kummalanjilanga shitushite laga ku nkowa gwa ku Ashia kula, shilajesho shashinkututopela kwa kaje mpaka gutuwile mitima kuti tukalama.  
\v 9 Elo, mmitima jetu putwaliji mbuti bhandu bhaukumwilwenje kubhulagwa, nkupinga tunaikulupalile twaashayene, ikabhe twaakulupalile a Nnungu bhakwaayuyanga bhandu bhawilenje.  
\v 10 Bhenebho bhatutapwile nshilaje shikulungwa shapingaga kutubhulaga shila, na bhanapunda kututapula. Tunakwakulupalila kuti shibhatutapule kabhili.  
\v 11 Mmanganya nnakutujangutilanga kwa kutujujila. Nkupinga bhandu bhabhagwinji bhatendanje eja kwa a Nnungu ga ligongo lya mboka itupata kwa jujilwa na bhandu bhabhagwinji. 
\s1 Kutindiganyika kwa Mwanja gwa a Pauli 
\p  
\v 12 Shitukwiiniya shindu shimo, mitima jetu jinakutukong'ondelala kuti tunatama pa shilambolyo pano na kajekaje munkumbi gwenunji, kwa kwiitimalika kutupegwilwe na a Nnungu. Twangalongoywa na lunda lwetu ikabhe kwa nema ja a Nnungu.  
\v 13 Tunakunjandishilanga indu ishinkombolanje shoma na kwiimanya. Ngunakulupalila kuti shimwimanyanje ukoto,  
\v 14 pabha nnaino mmumanyinji kashoko. Bhai, tumumanyi kuti lyubha lya kwiya a Yeshu shumwiiniyanje kwa ligongo lyetu malinga shitukwiiniya uwe kwa ligongo lyenunji. 
\p  
\v 15 Ngulikulupalila kumanya na kulupalila kwenunji, gundumbilile ndandubhe kuika kunngwenunji nkupinga mpwaikanje pabhili.  
\v 16 Natumbilile mbitile kungwenunji gwa kwenda na gwa nkubhuja kunkoa gwa Makedonia, nkupinga nnyangutilanje ga mwanja gwangu gwa kwenda ku Yudea. 
\p  
\v 17 Bhuli, punkuganishiyanga kuti naliji mundu jwa pindikukapindikuka? Eu, punkuganishiyanga njitumbilila kwa lunda lwangupe? Kuti ngunabheleketa “Elo” na “Nngabha” gwanakamo?  
\v 18 A Nnungu bha kweli jika, bhai, shitummalanjilenje shila nngabha shindu sha “Elo” na “Nngabha”  
\v 19 Pabha a Kilishitu bhanabhabho a Nnungu, bhutunnungushiyenje nne na a Shilibhanushi na a Timoteo, bhakaliji bha “Elo” na “Nngabha.” Ikabhe mobha gowe bhenebho ni “Elo” ja a Nnungu.  
\v 20 Pabha malagano gowe ga a Nnungu gali mwa a Kilishitu ni ga “Elo” kwa lyene ligongolyo, “Amina” jetu pujilugulwa kwa lina lya a Yeshu nkwaakuya a Nnungu. 
\p  
\v 21 Bhai a Nnungu bhayene bhanakutushimilika uwe pamo na mmanganya nkulundana na a Kilishitu. Na kutuagula,  
\v 22 bhenebho gubhatupele Mbumu jwabho mmitima jetu abhe lulembo kuti uwe tubhabho na abhe ngamulo ja indu yowe ibhatubhishile. 
\p  
\v 23 A Nnungu ni bhakong'ondela bhangu ngaabheleketa unami, gundumbilile ngunaishe kabhili ku Kolinto ngunakummulayanga kuinjika kwa malobhe ga kalipa.  
\v 24 Tukaapinga kunshishilishiyanga ga indu inkukulupalilanga, pabha mwiishimilikenje nngulupai jenunji. Ikabhe uwe tubhaajangutila bha angalala kwenunji. 
\c 2  
\p  
\v 1 Bhai, njitumbilila ngunanng'owelanje kabhili ngunakummulayanga kuinjika.  
\v 2 Pabha nimmulayangaga kuinjika, bhai, gani shaang'angalaye? Ikabhe mmanganya bhunimuleyenje kuinjika.  
\v 3 Nannjandishilenje nneyo, nkupinga pushing'ishepo ngunainjishe ga bhene bhapinjikwangaga kung'angalaya. Nne nimumanyi kuti inonyelaga na mmanganya shiinnonyelanje.  
\v 4 Punannjandishilenje pala munaliji nshilaje shikulungwa muntima na minyoi jilitunguka, nngabha kuti nng'injikanje, ikabhe mmumanyanje shinguti kumpinjiyanga. 
\s1 Kunneshelela Nkulebha 
\p  
\v 5 Na nnaino apali mundu ammuleye nnjakwe kuinjika, jwangamulaya kuinjika nnepe, ikabheje mmowenji mmwe, numbe ngunapunde bheleketa.  
\v 6 Ukumu jimumpelenje mmandu bhabhagwinji jinakumpwaa.  
\v 7 Bhai mbaya munneshelelanje jwene mundujo, na muntaganje ntima nkupinga anainjishe niwa ntima.  
\v 8 Kwa nneyo ngunakunshondelesheyanga, munnanguyanje kuti nnakumpinganga kwa kaje.  
\v 9 Shinatumbilile kunnjandishilanga mbhaluwa mula, nkupinga nole monaga shinkundanje indu yowe.  
\v 10 Munneshelelangaga mundu shindu shoshowe, numbe nne ninneshelele, monaga shipali kweli shindu shoshowe sha leshelela, ngunakunneshelela pa meyo ga a Kilishitu kwa ligongo lyenunji,  
\v 11 nkupinga Lishetani anatupunde, pabha tugumanyi ugulumba gwakwe. 
\s1 A Pauli Kushilambo sha Toloa 
\p  
\v 12 Ngaisheje kushilambo sha ku Toloa kuulunguya Ngani ja Mmbone ja a Kilishitu, Bhakulungwa bhashinkutenda ngombole kukamula liengo ukoto.  
\v 13 Ikabheje nashinkutenguka pabha nangaabhona ajetu a Tito. Gunaalajilenje bhandunji bha penepo nigumbite ku Makedonia. 
\s1 Kukombola kwa Jangutilwa na a Kilishitu 
\p  
\v 14 Ikabheje, bhatendelwe eja a Nnungu bhakututenda mobha gowe tukombole kutama nkulundana na a Kilishitu. Numbe nibhakututenda tujeneye Ngani ja a Kilishitu mbuti indu ya nunjila mmbali yowe.  
\v 15 Pabha uwe mbuti nunjila kwa lubhani lwa a Kilishitu kwa a Nnungu, munkumbi gwa bhowe bhaatapulwanga na bhaobhanga.  
\v 16 Kwa bhaobhanga bhala kwene kunnunjilako kwa shiwo, ikabheje kubhaatapulwanga kwene kununjilako kunataga gumi. Bhai, gani shapwae kwa lyene liengolyo?  
\v 17 Uwe nngabha malinga bhatendelanga upindi ntenga gwa a Nnungu, ikabhe tunalunguya kwa ntima gwa uguja pa meyo ga a Nnungu, malinga bhandu tutumilwe na a Nnungu, tulundene na a Kilishitu. 
\c 3  
\s1 Bhakamula Maengo bha Malagano ga Ambi 
\p  
\v 1 Bhuli, tunatandubha kwiiniya kabhili twaashayene? Bhuli, tunapinga bhaluwa ja lumanyio malinga shiikupinjikwa ku bhandu bhananji pubhakwiyangananga kunngwenunji eu kopoka kunngwenunji?  
\v 2 Mmwe mwaashayene ni bhaluwa jetu, bhaluwa jijandishwe mmitima jetu, na jinamanyika na shomwa na bhandu bhowe.  
\v 3 Mmanyikenje kuti mmanganya bhaluwa ja a Kilishitu kukopoka mmakono getu. Bhaluwa jijandishwe nngabha na wino, ikabhe kwa Mbumu jwa a Nnungu bhali bhakwete gumi, nngabha jijandishwe nshipande sha liganga, ikabhe mmitima ja bhandu. 
\p  
\v 4 Tunakombola bheleketa genego gwangali bhoga pa meyo ga a Nnungu, ligongo lya ngulupai itukwete kwa a Nnungu kwa gene gubhatendile a Yeshu Kilishitu gala.  
\v 5 Nngabha tunakombola tenda shindu shoshowe kwa mashili getu, ikabhe mashili getu kugakopoka kwa a Nnungu.  
\v 6 Pabha bhenebho bhatutendile uwe kulunguya malagano ga ambi, nngabha malagano ga Shalia jijandikwe, ikabhe malagano gaka Mbumu jwa a Nnungu. Pabha Shalia jinabhulaga, ikabhe Mbumu anataga gumi. 
\s1 Ukonjelo gwa Malagano ga Ambi 
\p  
\v 7 Shalia jashinkujandikwa mwiipande ya maganga. Ikabhe mpelo gwakwe shiwo, ukonjelo gwabho gwashinkupunda mpaka bha Ishilaeli bhashinkulepelanga kwaalola a Musha kumeyo, ligongo lya ng'anyima kwabho. Kung'anyima kwabho kwangalonjeya. Bhai, ibhaga Shalia jipeleshela kuwa jatendeshe kwa ukonjelo gwa nneyo,  
\v 8 bhuli, liengo lika Mbumu jwa a Nnungu likapunda kukola ukonjelo?  
\v 9 Bhai, ibhaga gwashinkupagwa ukonjelo nniengo lya ukumula ukoto, penepo liengo lipeleshela uguja shilibhe na ukonjelo gwa puya.  
\v 10 Ukonjelo gwalongolele gula ushipela, pabha nnaino shikwete ukonjelo gwa puya, shiishe.  
\v 11 Ibhaga shene shaliji sha pitape shashinkukola ukonjelo, lyakwa lipamba kuti sha pitipiti shila shipinga kola ukonjelo gwa puya. 
\p  
\v 12 Na pabha shitukulupalila ni sheneshi, uwe tunabheleketa kwa mashili.  
\v 13 Uwe tukatenda malinga a Musha bhaiunishile nngubho kumeyo, nkupinga bha Ishilaeli bhanakubhonanje kung'anyima kwabho kulipela.  
\v 14 Ikabhe lunda lwabhonji lwashinkupuganyika. Mpaka lelo Bhaishilaeli pubhaashomanga itabhu ya Malagano ga Bhukala, shitabhosho shikanabhe shoka. Pushishoka mundu alundanaga na a Kilishitu.  
\v 15 Elo, mpaka lelo kila pubhaashomanga itabhu ya a Musha, lunda lwabhonji lunapuganyika. 
\p  
\v 16 Ikabheje, malanga gogowe mundu pakwatendebhushila Bhakulungwa a Yeshu, shitabhosho shinashoywa.  
\v 17 Bhai, “Bhakulungwa” ni Mbumu na popowe pali Mbumu jwa Bhakulungwa penepo pa ungwana.  
\v 18 Bhai, uwe tubhowe twangaunishilwa kumeyo, tunalangula ukonjelo gwa Bhakulungwa mbuti kung'anyima kwa shioo, shitutindiganywe tulandane na Bhakulungwa, tulishoka ukonjelo kwenda ukonjelo guna, numbe gwa puya. Lyene liengolyo lika Mbumu jwa Bhakulungwa. 
\c 4  
\s1 Shibhiko sha Kunnungu Mwikelelo ya Lilongo 
\p  
\v 1 Bhai, a Nnungu kwa shiya shabho, bhashikutupa liengo lino, kwa nneyo tukawa ntima.  
\v 2 Tushileka indu yowe ya tokomaya na ya nng'iyo. Tukatama kabhili muunami, eu nkulipuganya lilobhe lya a Nnungu, ikabhe kwa lunguya ya kweli gwangali nng'iyo, tunakwaalanguyanga bhandunji bhamumanyanje mmitima jabhonji kuti tunatenda ibhapinga a Nnungu.  
\v 3 Pabha, monaga Ngani ja Mmbone jitulunguyaji jishikwiiya, bhai jishikwiiya ku bhaobhanga.  
\v 4 Bhalabhonji bhakaakulupalilanga pabha Lishetani, nnungu jwa shilambolyo ashikwaapuganyanga lunda lwabhonji bhanashibhonanje shilangaya sha Ngani ja Mmbone ja Ukonjelo gwa a Kilishitu, bhali malinga shibhali a Nnungu.  
\v 5 Pabha tukakwilunguya twaashayene, ikabhe bhutukwalunguya a Kilishitu kuti Bhakulungwa na uwe tubhatumishi bhenunji kwa ligongo lya a Kilishitu.  
\v 6 Pabha a Nnungu bhabhelekete, “Shilangaya shilangaye nnubhindu,” bhai bhenebho shibhalangaye mitima jetu, na kutupa shilangaya sha kuumanya ukonjelo gwa a Nnungu gulangaya kumeyo kwa a Kilishitu. 
\p  
\v 7 Ikabheje, uwe tuli na shene shibhikosho, putuli mbuti indu ya lilongo ibhishilwe indu ya muntima, nkupinga imanyishe kuti mashili gamakulungwa ni ga a Nnungu na nngabha getu.  
\v 8 Mobha gowe tunalaga, ikabheje tukaamaliywa. Tunakola lipamba, ikabheje tukawa ntima,  
\v 9 tunalaga, ikabheje tukalekwa gwangali jangutilwa. Nkali bhatugalabhuyanje pai tukaabhulagwa.  
\v 10 Mobha gowe tunaowa na shiwo sha a Yeshu mwiilu yetu, nkupinga gumi gwabho gubhoneshe mwiilu yetu.  
\v 11 Elo, pututama pano shiwo shinakutukagula ligongo lya kwaakamulila liengo a Kilishitu, nkupinga gumi gwabho gubhoneshe mwiilu yetu yawa ino.  
\v 12 Malombolelo gakwe ni kuti, uwe tukaajogopa nkali kuwa, nkupinga mmanganyanji mpatanje gumi gwa pitipiti. 
\p  
\v 13 Ishijandikwa Mmajandiko ga Ukonjelo, “Nne ngulupalile, kwa nneyo ngunabheleketa.” Numbe uwe nneyo peyo, tubhaga na ntima gogo pego gwa ngulupai, tunakulupalila na kwa lyene ligongolyo tunabheleketa.  
\v 14 Tumumanyi kuti a Nnungu bhaayushiye Bhakulungwa a Yeshu bhala, shibhatuyuye na uwe pamo na a Yeshu na kutubhika pa makongono gabho, pamo na mmanganya.  
\v 15 Gowego ni kwa ligongo lyenunji, nkupinga nema ja a Nnungu pushijipunde ku bhandu bhabhagwinji, kutenda eja kupunde na a Nnungu bhakuywe. 
\s1 Kutama Nngulupai 
\p  
\v 16 Kwa lyene ligongolyo tukawa ntima, nkali iilu yetu itutikaga, ikabhe mmitima jetu munabha mwaambi mobha gowe.  
\v 17 Pabha shilaje shetu nngabha sha punda, numbe sha malanga gashokope, ikabheje shinakutupa ukonjelo gwa puya kaje gwa pitipiti guli gwa mmbone kupunda shilaje shino.  
\v 18 Kwa nneyo tunalolele indu ibhoneka, ikabhe ikabhoneka. Pabha ibhoneka ikalonjeya, ikabheje ikabhoneka ila, ni ya pitipiti. 
\c 5  
\s1 Iilu ya Ambi 
\p  
\v 1 Pabha tumumanyi kuti iilu yetu ya pashilambolyo ino malinga liema, liangabhanywaga jipali nyumba jina jikopoka kwa a Nnungu jangashengwa na makono gaka mundu, shijibhe ja pitipiti.  
\v 2 Pabha mwiilu muno tunabhubhula, tulilokolila kupegwa iilu yetu ya ambi ili kunnungu.  
\v 3 Pabha tuwashwaga iilu ya kunnungu, tukabhoneka mbuti mbumu gwangali shiilu.  
\v 4 Tuli nshiilu sha pashilambolyo shino, tunabhubhula kwa topelwa, nngabha kuti tunapinga kuleka shiilu shawa shino, ikabheje tupegwe shiilu shikawa, nkupinga gumi gwa pitipiti utindiganye shiilu shetu shawa shila.  
\v 5 A Nnungu bhayene bhashikututendela yene mbindikuloi, gubhatupele Mbumu jwabho abhe ngamulo ja indu yowe ibhatubhishile. 
\p  
\v 6 Bhai, mobha gowe tunakulupalila, numbe tumumanyi kuti tutamaga na yene iilu ino mobha gowe, tunatalikangana na Bhakulungwa.  
\v 7 Pabha tunatama kwa ngulupai na nngabha kwa lola.  
\v 8 Elo, uwe twiishimilishe numbe tunabhona mbaya kushileka shiilu shino, nitama na Bhakulungwa.  
\v 9 Kwa nneyo shindu sha mmbone kupunda yowe, ni kutenda ibhapinga a Nnungu, tubhaga nshiilu sha pa shilambolyo, eu tubhaga nshiilu sha kweneko.  
\v 10 Tubhowe tunapinjikwa kujima pa shitengu sha ukumu sha a Kilishitu, nkupinga kila mundu aposhele malinga shatendaga mobha ga gumi gwakwe, gabhe ga uguja eu gangali ga mmbone. 
\s1 Kwaatendebhushila a Nnungu Kupitila a Yeshu Kilishitu 
\p  
\v 11 Bhai, tumumanyi kuti inapinjikwa kwaajogopa Bhakulungwa, penepo tunakwaakwiyanga bhandunji, ikabheje a Nnungu bhajimanyi mitima jetu na nne ngunakulupalila kuti na mmanganyanji ntumanyinji ukoto.  
\v 12 Pabha tukakwiiniya kungwenunji, ikabhe tunakumpanganga ligongo lya kwiiniya, nkupinga nkolanje sha kwajangulanga bhakwiiniyanga ga ibhakwibhonanga, kupunda ili mmitima jabhonji.  
\v 13 Ibhaga tuubhoneka tukwete shalubha, genego ni kwa ligongo lya kwaanonyeya a Nnungu, eu ibhaga tukwete lunda genego ni kwa ligongo lyenunji.  
\v 14 Pabha kupinga kwabho a Kilishitu kunakutulongoya uwe tukulupalile kuti, mundu jumo ashinkuwa kwa ligongo lya bhowe, bhai bhowe bhawilenje pamo na jwenejo.  
\v 15 Bhashinkuwa kwa ligongo lya bhowe, nkupinga bhabhakotonji bhanaikulupalilanje ashaayenenji, ikabheje kwa bhene bhawile na yuywa kwa ligongo lyabhonji. 
\p  
\v 16 Bhai, tandubhila nnaino, tukakunnola mundu kwa lunda lwa shigundu. Nkali uwe twaabhweni a Kilishitu shigundu, ikabheje nnaino tukakwaabhona shana nneyo.  
\v 17 Bhai ibhaga mundu alundanaga na a Kilishitu anabha mundu jwa ambi, ga bhukala gapitile nnaino gaishe ga ambi.  
\v 18 Yowe kuikopoka kwa a Nnungu, bhatupatanishe uwe na bhenebho kwa shiwo sha a Kilishitu, gubhatupele liengo lya kwaapatanishanga bhananji na a Nnungu.  
\v 19 Ntenga gwetu ni kuti, a Nnungu bhashinkwiipatanisha na bhandunji bha shilambolyo kwa shiwo sha a Yeshu, gwangali kuitolelela ilebho ya bhandunji, gubhatupele liengo lya kwaapatanishanga bhandunji na bhenebho. 
\p  
\v 20 Kwa nneyo, uwe tubhantenga bha a Kilishitu. Na a Nnungu bhayene bhanakunshemanga mmanganyanji kupitila uwe. Kwa nneyo, tunakunnjuganga kwa lina lya a Yeshu mpatananje na a Nnungu.  
\v 21 A Kilishitu bhakakweteje ilebho, ikabheje a Nnungu gubhaatendile bhaijigale ilebho yetu, nkupinga uwe nkulundana na a Kilishitu tukole aki kwa a Nnungu. 
\c 6  
\p  
\v 1 Bhai uwe tubhaga tubhakamula liengo pamo na a Nnungu, tunakunshondelesheyanga nnaposhelanje nema ja a Nnungu pa yoyo.  
\v 2 Pabha a Nnungu Mmajandiko ga Ukonjelo bhakuti, 
\q1 “Malanga ga pwaa nampilikanishiye, 
\q1 malanga ga ntapulo nannjangutile.” 
\m Bhai nnole, nnaino ni malanga ga pwaa, na lyubha lya ntapulo ni lelo. 
\s1 Shilaje sha a Pauli 
\p  
\v 3 Tukaapinga kubha shigwegwe kuka mundu jojowe, wala kwaatendanga bhandunji bhatugambanje nniengo lyetu.  
\v 4 Ikabheje, kwa kila shindu tulanguye kuti tubhatumishi bha a Nnungu, tulikwiipililila mmobha ga laga na mmboteko na nshilaje.  
\v 5 Nkukomwa na Nkutabhwa na nkutendelwa pujo, na tokoteka maengo, tushisheya na laga shibhanga.  
\v 6 Tuilanguye kuti tubhatumishi bha a Nnungu kwa mitima ja takata, na kwa lumanyio na kwa kwipililila na kwa uguja, kwa Mbumu jwa Ukonjelo, na nkupingana kwa kweli,  
\v 7 na nkulunguya ntenga gwa kweli, na kwa mashili ga a Nnungu. Ikomanilo yetu ya komanilana na ya kwiitapulila ni itendi ya aki.  
\v 8 Nkuishimiwa eu kwa nyegaywa, kwa gambwa eu kwa lumbililwa. Tuliganishiwa mbuti tubhanami, mbena itubheleketa ya kweli.  
\v 9 Tunabhoneka mbuti tukamanyika mbena tunamanyika na bhowe, tulibhoneka mbuti bhawilenje, mbena tubhabhakoto, tulikomwa ikabheje tukaabhulagwa.  
\v 10 Mbuti tushiinjika ikabheje tunaangalala mobha gowe. Mbuti twangali indu, mbena tunakwapanganga bhandu bhabhagwinji indu, tunabhoneka mbuti twangali shindu shoshowe, mbena tukwete indu yowe. 
\p  
\v 11 Mmanganya Bhakolinto, tunabheleketa na mmanganyanji kopoka mmitima jetu.  
\v 12 Uwe twangaleka kumpinganga mmanganyanji, ikabheje mmanganyanji nshikananga kutupinga uwe.  
\v 13 Bhai, nnaino ngunabheleketa na mmanganyanji mbuti ashibhanangu, bhai ntupinganje malinga shitukumpinganga. 
\s1 Nnalundananje na Bhakaakulupalilanga 
\p  
\v 14 Nnapangananje mbwiga na bhandunji bhakakwakulupalilanga a Kilishitu. Bhuli, aki na yangali ya mmbone inapatana? Shilangaya na lubhindu inatama pamo?  
\v 15 Bhuli a Kilishitu bhanapatana naka Lishetani? Eu akulupalila anapatana na akaakulupalila?  
\v 16 Likanisha jipatana bhuli na kuitindibhalila yanamu? Pabha uwe likanisha bhali bhakoto. Malinga shibhashite bheleketa a Nnungu bhayene, 
\q1 “Shindame mmitima jabhonji, 
\q1 na tama munkumbi gwabhonji. 
\q1 Shime Nnungu jwabhonji, 
\q1 na bhalabhonji shibhabhanganje bhandunji bhangu.” 
\m  
\v 17 Kwa nneyo Bhakulungwa bhakuti, 
\q1 “Nshokangananje munkumbi gwabhonji 
\q1 nnabhandikane nabhonji. 
\q1 Nnakwayanje shindu sha nyata, 
\q1 na nne shinimposhelanje. 
\q1  
\v 18 Nne 
\q1 shime na ng'inagwenunji, 
\q1 na mmanganya shimmanganje ashibhanangu bhanabhalume na bhanabhakongwe, bhanabheleketa Bhakulungwa Bhakwete Mashili.” 
\c 7  
\p  
\v 1 Bhai, ashaambwiga ajangunji, ibhaga tupegwilwe jene miadi joweji, twiitakaye na yowe inyatiya shiilu na mbumu, tubhe na ukonjelo na tutame kwa kwaishimiya a Nnungu. 
\s1 Kuangalala kwa a Pauli 
\p  
\v 2 Tunakunnjuganga ntuposhelanje mmitima jenunji! Tukanabhe kunnebhela mundu jojowe, wala tukanabhe kumpokonyola mundu wala kumpuganya mundu jojowe.  
\v 3 Ngaabheleketa gegano nkupinga ninng'ukumulanje mmanganya. Malinga shinjite bheleketa, mmanganya munninginji mmitima jetu, nkali kwa wa eu kwa lama pamo na mmanganya.  
\v 4 Ngunakunkulupalilanga mmanganya, nshilaje shetu nnandaganga ntima na nnang'angalayaga kwa kaje. 
\p  
\v 5 Nkali tukaisheje ku Makedonia twangapumulila. Ikabhe twashinkulaga mmbali yowe, palanga mipwai na mmitima lipamba.  
\v 6 Ikabheje a Nnungu, bhakwaataganga ntima bhawilenje ntima, bhashinkututaga ntima kwa kwiya kwabho a Tito.  
\v 7 Nngabha kwa ika kwabhope a Tito, ikabheje shinshite kwaataganga ntima. Bhatubhalanjile shinkuti lokolilanga kumona, na shinshite injikanga na shinkutumbililanga kunyanguta. Lyenelyo linandenda ng'angalale kaje. 
\p  
\v 8 Bhai, ibhaga mwainjikenje ga bhaluwa jangu, ngakwigamba. Nkali nneyo naigambile kashoko pabha namumanyi kuti mwashinkuinjikanga kashoko ga bhaluwa jila.  
\v 9 Ikabheje nnaino ngunakwinonyela, nngabha pabha nshiinjikanga, ikabhe mwashinkuinjikanga mpaka nikwiipeta. Pabha mwashinkuinjikanga malinga shibhapinjile a Nnungu na kwa lyene ligongolyo twangampotekanga kwa shoshowe.  
\v 10 Pabha kuinjika kubhaapinga a Nnungu kunakuntendebhuya mundu ntima nikumpa ntapulo, kwa nneyo lyakwa ligongo lya kwiigamba. Ikabheje kuinjika malinga kwa bhandunji bha pa shilambolyo, kunabhulaga.  
\v 11 Nnolanje shikoposhele nkuinjika kwenunji malinga shibhapinjile a Nnungu, nshibhanganga bhandu bha tumbila, na kulanguya kuti mwangalebhanga, na bha kunda. Nnaimukanga, na kupotekwa mitima, na nnalokolilanga kumona, na nnapingana, na nnapinganga kuukumula kwa aki. Kwa gene gowego nnangwiyenje kuti shakwa shinnebhilenje. 
\p  
\v 12 Bhai, ibhaga najandishe, nngabha kwa ligongo lika jwene alebhilejo eu alebhelwejo. Ikabhe nashinkutumbilila jandika imanyishe kwa a Nnungu shinkuti kwiishoyanga kwa ligongo lyetu uwe.  
\v 13 Kwa gene gowega tushitagwa ntima. 
\p Kupunda kutagwa ntima kwetu, twashinkuangalala kwa ligongo lya angalala kwa a Tito kwa shimwashite kwaangalayanga ntima mmowenji.  
\v 14 Nne njikunnumbililanga kubhenebho, kwa lyenelyo mwangandokomayanga. Tushikunnugulilanga kweli mobha gowe na kwene kunnumbililanga kwa ligongo lya a Tito ishibha ya kweli jika.  
\v 15 Kumpinganga kwabho kunapunda pubhakumbushila kukunda kwenunji mmowe shimwashite kwaaposhelanga kwa ishima ja kaje.  
\v 16 Ngunakwinonyela pabha inatendeka kunkulupalilanga mmanganya kwa indu yowe. 
\c 8  
\s1 Ntuka gwa Shikilishitu 
\p  
\v 1 Ashaalongo ajetu, tunapinga mmumanyanje ga nema ja a Nnungu jibhaapelenje makanisha ga ku Makedonia.  
\v 2 Nkali bhashinkulingwanga kwa mboteko yaigwinji, ikabheje kuangalala kwabhonji kwashinkupunda, nipeleshela kukola ntuka nankali nkulaga kwabhonji.  
\v 3 Ngunakong'ondela kuti bhashinkukolanga ntuka kupunda ibhakwetenje nkali bhakakwetenjeje indu yaigwinji, kwa engwa bhashinkushoyanga indu yabhonji malinga shibhakombwelenje.  
\v 4 Bhashinkutujuganga bhabhanganje bhatumishi na uwe ga kwaajangutanga bhandunji bha ukonjelo bha ku Yudea.  
\v 5 Bhashinkutendanga kupunda shitwaganishiye! Bhashinkutandubhanga kwiishoya ku Bhakulumgwa, kungai bhashinkwiishoyanga kwetu uwe malinga shibhapinjile bhayene a Nnungu.  
\v 6 Kwa nneyo, twashinkwashondelesheya a Tito pabha ni bhakumbwiye, bhannjangutilanje nkolanje ntima gwa ntuka, nkumalishiya lyene liengolyo.  
\v 7 Ikabheje mmanganya malinga shinkwetenje indu yaigwinji, nkwetenje ngulupai na kombola bheleketa na lumanyio na tumbila kowe kwa tenda ya mmbone na kutupinga kwenunji. Kwa nneyo, tunalolela mmanganje na uguja nkwiishoya kwenunji. 
\p  
\v 8 Ngakunng'amulishanga, ikabhe ngunapinga nimumanye kupingana kwenunji monaga kuli kwa kweli, kwa linganya na kupingana kwa bhananji.  
\v 9 Pabha mmanganya nnjimanyinji nema ja Bhakulungwa bhetu a Yeshu Kilishitu, shibhaitendile bhaalaga kwa ligongo lyenunji, ikabhe bhakwete indu, nkupinga mmanganya nkolanje indu kwa laga kwabho.  
\v 10 Bhai kwa lyeneli, ngunakunnugulilanga, inapwaa nnaino ntendanje gumwatandwibhenje kutenda masheyo gala. Mmanganyanji pumwalinginji bhantai kushoya, na kola lilaka lya tenda nneyo.  
\v 11 Bhai, mmaliyanje liengolyo, malinga shimwatumbililenje. Na kwa lilaka lila pelila mmaliyanje liengolyo kwa shoya malinga munkukombolelanga kushoya.  
\v 12 Pabha mundu akolaga ntima gwa shoya, a Nnungu bhanaposhela shoshowe shakwete mundu, na nngabha shatubhilwe. 
\p  
\v 13 Tukaatumbilila kuti mmanganya mpundanje kulaga, nkupinga bhananji bhapokanje, ikabheje ilingane.  
\v 14 Ikabhe nnaino, gwinji gwa indu inkwetenje, ujangutile bhaalaga, nkupinga na bhalabhonji pushibhakolanje ya punda, kubhannjangutilanje mmanganyanji, nkupinga nningane.  
\v 15 Malinga shiijandikwe Mmajandiko ga Ukonjelo, 
\q1 “Alopwele yaigwinji jwangali sha punda, 
\q1 na alopwele ishoko jwangatubhilwa.” 
\s1 A Tito Bhanatumwa Kukolinto 
\p  
\v 16 Ikabheje ngunatenda eja kwa a Nnungu, bhaapele a Tito shilokoli muntima gwabho sha kunnjangutilanga mmanganyanji, malinga nne.  
\v 17 Nngabha kuti bhashinkukundape kujuga kwetu, ikabhe bhashinkukola lilaka likulungwa lya jangutila mpaka gubhajabhwile kwiya kweneko kwa engwa bhayene.  
\v 18 Pamo na bhenebho, tunakuntuma mpwetu jumo ainiywa na makanisha gowe nniengo lya kwiya Ngani ja Mmbone jilunguywe.  
\v 19 Nngabha nneyope, ikabhe bhashiagulwa na makanisha bhalongane na uwe mmwanja gwa kamilisha liengo lya shoya kwa ntima gwa ntuka, litutenda kwa ukonjelo gwa Bhakulungwa. 
\p  
\v 20 Tunapinga kwiembuya tunagambwe na bhandunji, ga indu yaigwinji itugoyai.  
\v 21 Pabha tunatumbilila tenda ya aki, nngabha pa meyo ga Bhakulungwape, ikabheje nkali kubhandunji. 
\p  
\v 22 Bhai, pamo na ashaapwangabho, tunakuntuma mpwetu juna jutunninjile papagwinji na ashilangula kuti ashikola lilaka lya tumika, numbe anakunkulupalilanga kwa kaje.  
\v 23 Numbe a Tito ni ajangu nne, tunatenda liengo kwa ligongo lyenunji, na ga ashaapwetu bhananji bhakwiyangana na a Tito, ni bhantenga bha makanisha, bhanatendanga liengo kwa ukonjelo gwa a Kilishitu.  
\v 24 Bhai, nnanguyanje kumakanisha kuti nnakwaapinganga gwangali ugulumba, nkupinga makanisha gabhonji gabhone kuti kunkulupalilanga kwetu kutukwiiniya, ni kwa kweli. 
\c 9  
\s1 Kwaajangutilanga Bhakilishitu 
\p  
\v 1 Ga liengo lyenunji lya kwaapeleshelanga indu bhandunji bha ukonjelo bha ku Yudea ngakulibhona ligongo lya kunnjandishilanga kabhili.  
\v 2 Nimumanyi shinshite kolanga ntima gwa jangutila, na naitapile ga lyenelyo ku bhandunji bha ku Makedonia nilinkuti, “Ashaalongo ajetu bha ku Akaya bhatandubhenje kushoya kuumila masheyo.” Kwa nneyo, kutenda kwenunji kushikwaakwiyanga bhandu bhabhagwinji bhapundanje kushoya.  
\v 3 Bhai, njikwatumanga ashaalongo ajetubho, nkupinga kuitapa kwetu kunabhe malobhe jika, ikabhe kubhoneshe kutumbilila kwenunji nkujangutila malinga shinjite bheleketa.  
\v 4 Inabhe kuti bhandunji bha ku Makedonia pushibhaikangananje na nne nikunng'imananga nkanabhe bhanganga tayali, shitujiye kola oni kupunda oni jishinkolanje mwaashayene, pabha twankulupalilenje kwa kaje.  
\v 5 Kwa nneyo, njibhona inapinjikwa twaajuganje ashaalongo ajetubha, bhalongolelanje kwiya kunngwenunji, nkupinga bhabhikanje tayali indu ya jangutila, inkupinga shoyanga kwa engwa kwenunji. Yenei ibhaga tayali, shiilanguye kuti nshishoyanga kwa engwa na nngabha kwa shishilishiywa. 
\p  
\v 6 Nkumbushilanje kuti, apanda ishoko ashaune ishoko, apanda yaigwinji ashaune yaigwinji.  
\v 7 Bhai, kila mundu ashoye malinga shaengwilwe muntima na nngabha kwa injika eu kwa shishilishiwa, pabha a Nnungu bhanakumpinga mundu ashoya kwa angalala.  
\v 8 Na a Nnungu bhanakombola kumpanganga indu ya punda inkupinganga, nkupinga mobha gowe nkolanje indu inkwiipinganga, mpundanje kujangutila maengo gowe ga mmbone.  
\v 9 Malinga shigalugula Majandiko ga Ukonjelo, 
\q1 “Bhenebho bhashilaguya kwa punda, 
\q1 bhashikwaapanganga bhaalaga. 
\q1 Aki jabho jinalonjeya pitipiti.” 
\p  
\v 10 A Nnungu ni bhakumpa mmbeju nkupanda na nkate kubha shalya, shibhampanganje mmbeju inkupinganga na kwiitenda imele nikumpanganga mauno gamagwinji nkupinga ntima gwenunji gwa ntuka upunde.  
\v 11 Kwa nneyo shimmanganje matajili kwa indu yowe, nkupinga mobha gowe bhandunji bhaatendelanje eja a Nnungu, kwa ligongo lya ntuka gwenunji.  
\v 12 Pabha liengo lya shoya linkutendangali nngabha kwa jangutilape bhandunji bha ukonjelo, ikabheje bhandunji bhabhagwinji shibhapundanje kutenda eja kwa a Nnungu. 
\p  
\v 13 Kwa ligongo lya ukong'ondelo gwa lyene liengoli, bhandu shibhaakuyanje a Nnungu kwa ligongo lya kunda kwenunji, na kong'ondela ga Ngani ja Mmbone ja a Kilishitu, na ntuka gunkwaatendelanga bhanganyabho na bhandu bhowe.  
\v 14 Kwa nneyo shibhannjujilanje kwa a Nnungu, kwa ntima gwa kumpinganga, kwa ligongo lya nema jimpegwilwelenje na a Nnungu.  
\v 15 Tutende eja kwa a Nnungu kwa ligongo lya upo yabho yangali sha landanya! 
\c 10  
\s1 A Pauli Bhanabheleketa ga Liengo Lyabho 
\p  
\v 1 Bhai, nne a Pauli namwene ngunakunshondelesheyanga kwa tungamana na uguja malinga gwa a Kilishitu, nne nili jwa kwiitimalika pungubha na mmanganya, ikabheje na jwa makangala ga bheleketa, pungubha kwa talika na mmanganya  
\v 2 Ngunakunnjuganga nnamulayanje melekete kwa makangala pushing'ishepo, pabha nimumanyi kuti shindende nneyo ku bhandunji bhakutuganishiyanga kuti tunaakaguya ikubho ya pa shilambolyo.  
\v 3 Nankali tutama pa shilambolyo, ikabheje tukaakomana ngondo malinga shibhakomananga bhandunji bha pa shilambolyo.  
\v 4 Pabha, ikomanilo ya nngondo jetu nngabha malinga ikomanilo ya pa shilambolyo, ikabhe ishikola mashili ga a Nnungu ga kombola kuangabhanya mashili ga bhamagongo. Tunaangabhanya ng'aniyo ya unami,  
\v 5 na angabhanya ng'aniyo yowe ya kwiiniya, ibhishilwe nkupinga kutauka lumanyiyo lwa a Nnungu, tulikwiitenda ng'aniyo yowe yaakunde a Kilishitu.  
\v 6 Na shitubhe tayali kuukumula shitendi shoshowe sha tauka, kukunda kwenunji kukamilikaga. 
\p  
\v 7 Mmanganyanji nnalolanga indu kwa palangape. Bhuli, apali mundu jojowe aganishiya kuti jwenejo jwa a Kilishitu? Bhai, atuganishiye na uwe kuti tubha a Kilishitu malinga shali jwenejo.  
\v 8 Bhai, nkali niitapaga kashoko kwa ligongo lya mashili gutupegwilwe na Bhakulungwa, ga kunshimilikanga nngulupai na nngabha ga kunng'angabhanyanga, kwa nneyo ngakola oni.  
\v 9 Ngapinga nnganishiyanje kuti ngunapinga kunnjogoyanga kwa bhaluwa yangu.  
\v 10 Pabha bhananji bhakutinji, “Bhaluwa ya a Pauli inakalipa na ishikola malobhe ga topa, ikabhe bhayene bhabhaga na uwe bhakakola makangala, nkali malobhe gabho gakakola mashili.”  
\v 11 Mundu jwa nneyo amumanye kuti, itujandika mmaluwa tubhaga kwatalika, yoyo peyo itutenda putuika kunngwenunji. 
\p  
\v 12 Kwa kweli tukalinga kwiibhika eu kwiilinganya na bhandunji bhakwiiniyanga ashaayenenji. Ikabheje bhakwiipimanga na kwiilinganya ashayenenji kwa ashayenenji ni bhangumba.  
\v 13 Nkali nneyo, uwe tukakwiiniya kwa punda, ikabhe kwiiniya kwetu shikubhe nniengo libhatupele a Nnungu, kwa liengo litutenda mpaka kunng'ishilanga mmanganyanji.  
\v 14 Twangaiiniya kwa punda, pabha putwaishe kungwenunji kulunguya Ngani ja Mmbone ja a Kilishitu, twangapunda mipika.  
\v 15 Bhai, tukakwiiniya kwa liengo libhatendilenje bhananji, ikabhe tunaakulupalila kuti ngulupai jenunji shijipunde, na liengo lyetu shilipunde kujenjesheka munkumbi gwenunji, gwangali pelenganya mipika jitubhishilwe na a Nnungu.  
\v 16 Penepo shitulunguye Ngani ja Mmbone mwilambo ina, kwa nneyo shitwiiniye kwa ligongo lya liengo lyetu na nngabha libhatendilenje bhananji. 
\p  
\v 17 Ikabheje, malinga shigakuti lugula Majandiko ga Ukonjelo, “Jwene apinga kwiiniya, aiiniye kwa ligongo lya Bhakulungwa.”  
\v 18 Pabha mundu apingwa, nngabha akwiilumbilila nnyene, ikabhe alumbililwa na Bhakulungwa. 
\c 11  
\s1 A Pauli na Mitume bha Unami 
\p  
\v 1 Na mbaya mwiipilililanje kashoko ga ungumba gwangu! Elo, mwiipilililanje.  
\v 2 Njikola lupimililo genu mmanganyanji, malinga lwa a Nnungu, pabha mmanganya punninginji mbuti mwali akanabhe kummanya jwannume, junintomele kuka jwannume jumo, ni a Kilishitu.  
\v 3 Ikabheje ngunajogopa, inabha malinga lijoka jula, kwa unami gwakwe ashinkwaatemba a Awa kwa lunda lwakwe, ng'aniyo yenunji inapuganywe nileka kulupalika na kwiishoya kwenunji kwa a Kilishitu.  
\v 4 Pabha aikaga mundu juna nilunguya ngani ja a Yeshu bhanape, bhutukanakwaalunguya uwe, mmanganyanji nnakumposhelanga, na punda genego, nnakunkundanga mbumu juna eu Ngani ja Mmbone jina jikalandana na jimposhelenje kopoka kwetu uwe! 
\p  
\v 5 Ikabheje ngaganishiya kuti nne najwanshoko punda bhene bhashemwanga kwali, “Mitume bhakulu.”  
\v 6 Nkali ngaakombola bheleketa ukotoyo, ikabheje ngwete lumanyio, lyeneli tulangwiye kunngwenunji gwangali nng'iyo mmbali yowe na mobha gowe. 
\p  
\v 7 Nne nashinkunnungushiyanga Ngani ja Mmbone ja a Nnungu gwangali kulipwa, nashinkwiituluya nkupinga ninkweyanje mmanganyanji. Bhuli nashinkulebha?  
\v 8 Punatendaga liengo kungwenunji, natendaga pegwa indu na bhandunji bhana, eu melekete kuti, nashinkupokonyola indu yabhonji ninnjangutilanje mmanganyanji.  
\v 9 Punaliji na mmanganya nangannolela mundu jojowe ga shindu shoshowe, pabha Bhakilishitu ajetunji bhakopokenje ku Makedonia bhambelenje kila shindu shinapinjile. Nashinkwiteiga ngunannolele mundu kwa shoshowe na ngunapunda tenda nneyo.  
\v 10 Malinga shijili kweli ja a Kilishitu muntima gwangu, jwakwapi mundu shang'ibhilile mmbali yowe ya ku Akaya, ga kwiiniya kwangu.  
\v 11 Kwa nndi ngunabheleketa nneyo? Kuti kwa ligongo ngakumpinganga? Nngabha, a Nnungu bhamumanyi kuti ngulikumpinganga! 
\p  
\v 12 Na shimbunde kutenda malinga shingutenda nnaino shino, nkupinga naibhililanje bhene bhaaloleyanga kwiiniya, kuti bhanatendanga liengo malinga uwe.  
\v 13 Pabha, bhanganyabho ashimitume bha unami, bhakamula liengo bhanami, bhalikwiitembanga mbuti ashimitume bha kweli bha a Kilishitu.  
\v 14 Wala nngabha ga lapa, pabha nkali Lishetani nnyene anakwitemba mbuti malaika jwa shilangaya!  
\v 15 Kwa nneyo nngabha ga lapa, ibhaga bhatumishi bhakwe bhanakwiitendanga mbuti bhatumishi bhanguja pa meyo ga a Nnungu. Kumpelo shibhaukumulwanje kwa itendi yabhonji. 
\s1 Mboteko ya a Pauli ga Utume Gwabho 
\p  
\v 16 Kabhili nguti, mundu anang'anishiye kuti nanngumba. Ikabheje ntendangaga nneyo, bhai, nndolelelanje mbuti nanngumba nkupinga ngole sha kwiiniya kapela kashoko.  
\v 17 Shingubheleketa nnainoshi nngabha shibhapinga Bhakulungwa, ikabheje ga kwiiniyaga ngunabheleketa mbuti nngumba.  
\v 18 Pabha bhabhagwinjinji bhanakwiiniyanga kwa gene gubhatendilenje pa shilambolyo, numbe nne shiniiniye.  
\v 19 Mmanganya nkakwaapatanga bhangumba, pabha nshikolanga lunda!  
\v 20 Nnakuipilililanga nkali mundu ammikanje utumwa, eu akunnjibhanga, eu akunng'amulishanga, eu akunnyegayanga eu akunkomanga mapapa kumeyo!  
\v 21 Ngunakola oni kubheleketa kuti kwa genego twashinkwiinyegaya. 
\p Ikabheje malinga bhandunji bhana shibhalinganga kwiiniya ga shindu shoshowe, ngunabheleketa mbuti nngumba, numbe nne shiniiniye.  
\v 22 Bhuli, bhanganyabho Bhaebhulania? Nkali nne Muebhulania. Bhuli, bhanganyabho Bhaishilaeli? Nkali nne Mwishilaeli. Bhanganyabho lubheleko lwa a Bhulaimu? Nkali nne lubheleko lwa a Bhulaimu.  
\v 23 Bhalabhonji bhatumishi bha a Kilishitu? Shimelekete mbuti ngwete shalubha. Nkali nne nantumishi jwa a Kilishitu numbe kupunda bhanganyabho, nne njitenda liengo likulungwa, njitabhwa papagwinji, na njikomwa papagwinji, na papagwinji punaliji tome nawa.  
\v 24 Ku Bhayaudi nashinkukomwa paano, ndomondo makumi gatatu na tisha shalepeshe shimope iishile makumi nsheshe.  
\v 25 Nashinkukomwa imbo patatu na Bhaloma, na kamo nashinkukomwa maganga. Patatu meli jashinkundemeshela mbhaali, kamo natemi mmashi ga bhaali shilo na mui.  
\v 26 Papagwinji mmwanja gwangu njiimikana na ya jogoya, ya ndanje ya mashi, na ya jogoya ya bhaapokonyola, na ya jogoya kopoka ku bhashilambo ajangunji, na ya kopoka ku bhandunji bha ilambo ina, na ya jogoya ya mwiilambo, na ya mukonde, na ya mbhaali, na ya a Bhakilishitu ajetunji bha unami.  
\v 27 Nashinkulaga mmaengo ga topa, njisheya papagwinji. Njilaga shibhanga na nnjota, papagwinji natendaga tama gwangali kulya, njilaga mmbepo gwangali nngubho. 
\p  
\v 28 Na kupunda genego, mobha gowe ngunatopelwa na ng'aniyo ya liengo lya mmakanisha gowe.  
\v 29 Apagwaga mundu jwangali mashili na nne ngakola mashili, nneyo peyo mundu alebhaga, nne inamboteka. 
\p  
\v 30 Mbinjikwaga kwiiniya, bhai, shiniiniye kwa ungakola mashili gwangu.  
\v 31 A Nnungu, Ainabhabho Bhakulungwa bhetu a Yeshu, lina lyabho likuywe pitipiti, bhenebho bhamumanyi ngaabheleketa unami.  
\v 32 Punaliji ku Dameshiki, bhakulungwa bhamo bha a mpalume Aleta, bhashinkubhika ulinda pa shilambo nkupinga ngamulwe.  
\v 33 Ikabheje, nashinkutuluywa palanga nshikapu shikulungwa, kupitila pa lilanga lya nnikumba gunaatolweshe. 
\c 12  
\s1 Nng'ibhulo gwa Pauli na Mboteko Yabho 
\p  
\v 1 Bhai ngunapinga kwiiniya, nkali ikapwae! Ikabheje nnaino ngunapinga bheleketa ga mabhono na maibhulo gumbatile kopoka ku Bhakulungwa.  
\v 2 Nimmanyi mundu jumo abhakulupalile a Yeshu, yaka likumi limo na nsheshe ipitile, ashinkutolwa mpaka kunnungu kwataliya kaje. Ibhaga kweneko apiteje kwa shiilu eu kwa mbumu nne ngakumumanya, a Nnungu bhamumanyi.  
\v 3 Numbe nne ngunabhujila kubheleketa kuti, jwene mundujo monaga apite kwa shiilu eu kwa mbumu, nne ngakumumanya, ikabheje a Nnungu bhamumanyi.  
\v 4 Ashinkutolwa mpaka kupaladisho, kweneko ashinkupilikana indu ya nng'iyo ikapinjikwa mundu kutagulila.  
\v 5 Bhai, mbinga kwiiniya gaka mundu malinga jwenejo, ikabheje ngaiiniya gangu namwene, ikabhe kwa ungakola mashili gwangu.  
\v 6 Nkali ngapinjile kwiiniya nganabhe nangumba, pabha ngabhelekete ya kweli jika. Ikabheje ngaiiniya, nkupinga mundu anang'anishiye punda shinguti tenda na bheleketa. 
\p  
\v 7 Ikabheje nkupinga ngunaiiniye kwa gwene nng'ibhulo nkulugo, nashinkupegwa shindu sha poteka mbuti mibha nshiilu shangu kubha mbuti muntenga juka Lishetani amboteshe, nkupinga ngunapunde kwiiniya.  
\v 8 Kwa ligongo lya shene shindusho, nashinkwashondelesheya Bhakulungwa patatu nkupinga bhanjosheye shene shindusho.  
\v 9 Ikabheje gubhanugulile, “Nema jangu shijimpwae, pabha mashili gangu ganamalila muungakola mashili.” Bhai, ngunaengwa kwiiniya ga ungakola mashili gwangu, nkupinga mashili ga a Kilishitu gatame na nne.  
\v 10 Kwa nneyo ngunaengwa na ungakola mashili gwangu, na matukano, na shilaje na mboteko kwa ligongo lya a Kilishitu, pabha pungakola mashili, penepo ni pungubha na mashili. 
\s1 Lipamba lya a Pauli ga Bhakolinto 
\p  
\v 11 Njibha mbuti nangumba, ikabheje mmanganyanji nshindendanga mme nneyo. Mmanganyanji mwapinjikwenje kung'iniya nne. Pabha, ningabhe shindu shoshowe, nne nngabha najwanshoko punda bhene bhakwiishemanga “Mitume bhakulu.”  
\v 12 Itendi ya ilangulo na ilapo yashinkutendeka munkumbi gwenunji, ilanguya kuti nne ntume kwa kwiikakatimila kwa punda.  
\v 13 Bhuli, shindu shashi shintubhilwenje kupunda makanisha gana, ikabhe nne nangantotoyanga nkupinga nnyangutilanje? Shonde nneshelelanje kwa shinebhilesho! 
\p  
\v 14 Nnaino puni tayali kunng'owelanga gwatatu na ngantopelanga. Pabha shingupinga nngabha indu yenunji, ikabhe ngumpinganga mmanganyanji. Pabha, bhana bhakakwaabhishilanga shibhiko bhaakwetenje, ikabhe bhaakwetenje ni bhakwaabhishilanga shibhiko ashibhana bhabhonji.  
\v 15 Nne njiengwa kushoya yowe ingwete nkali kwiishoya namwene, nkupinga kunnjangutilanga mmanganyanji. Nkali ngumpinjiyangayo, mmanganya nnambinganga kashokope. 
\p  
\v 16 Bhai, nkundanje kuti nangantopelanga. Ikabheje bhandunji bhana shibhaganishiyanje kuti, pabha njikola lunda nimpatilenje kwa kuntekeyanga.  
\v 17 Bhuli, nne nantekeyenje indu yenunji kubhantenga bhunaatumilenje kunngwenunji?  
\v 18 Nne nashinkwaashondelesheya a Tito, gunaatumile kungwenunji naka mpwetu juna. Bhuli, a Tito bhantekeyenje? Bhuli, nkakumumanyanga kuti uwe tunalongoywa na ng'aniyo imo na itendi yetu imo? 
\p  
\v 19 Pana nnaganishiyanga kuti tunabheleketa nkwiitapula kungwenunji! Ikabheje, tunabheleketa genego pa meyo ga a Nnungu, tuli tulundene na a Kilishitu. Gene gowe gututendaga ashaapwetu, nkupinga kunshimilikanga.  
\v 20 Pabha ngunajogopa, pana pushing'ishe kunngwenunji ngang'imananga malinga shingupinga, na mmanganya nkamonanga malinga shinkupinganga. Ngunajogopa ngunakunng'imananga nninginji na mpwai, na lupimililo, na nnjimwa na kulambililana, na lung'wenyi na matukano, na kuipuna na nnjasha munkumbi gwenunji.  
\v 21 Ngunajogopa pushing'ishe mwanja gunago, a Nnungu bhangu shibhandende niitimalishe, shiniigutanjile kwa ligongo lya bhabhagwinji bhalebhilenje, ikabheje bhangaipetanga kwa ya nyata yabhonji na labhalabha kwabhonji na ilokoli yabhonji yangali ya mmbone ibhatendilenje. 
\c 13  
\s1 Maleyo ga Mpelebhesheyo na Shalamu 
\p  
\v 1 Gweguno mwanja gwangu gwa tatu gushing'ishe kungwenunji Malinga Majandiko ga Ukonjelo shigaabheleketa. “Ngani jojowe pujimala kwa ukong'ondelo gwa bhandu bhabhili eu bhatatu.”  
\v 2 Nannugulilenje, malinga mwanja gwangu gwa bhili, ngunakunnugulilanga kabhili nili kwataliya, bhatendilenje ilebho bhukala na bhananji bhowe, pushing'ishepo ngaabhonelanga shiya.  
\v 3 Shindende nneyo pabha mmanganyanji nnapinganga ukong'ondelo, kuti a Yeshu bhanabheleketa na mmanganyanji kupitila nne. Kwenu mmanganya a Kilishitu nngabha kuti bhangali mashili, ikabhe shibhalanguye mashili gabho munkumbi gwenunji.  
\v 4 Pabha pubhakomelwe munshalabha bhakakweteje mashili, ikabheje nnaino bhanaatama kwa mashili ga a Nnungu. Numbe na uwe twangali mashili nkulundana na bhenebho, ikabheje tunatama nabho kwa mashili ga a Nnungu, nkupinga tutende liengo munkumbi gwenunji. 
\p  
\v 5 Mwiibhuyanje mwaashayenenji monaga mwiishimilikenje nngulupai. Mwiibhuyanje mwaashayenenji. Bhuli, nkakumumanyanga kuti a Yeshu Kilishitu mubhali mmitima jenunji? Monaga nngabha, bhai nnepelenje.  
\v 6 Ikabheje ngunakulupalila kuti mmanganya mmumanyinji kuti uwe twangalepela.  
\v 7 Tunakwaajuga a Nnungu nnatendanje shangali sha mmbone shoshowe, nngabha tubhoneshe kuti tushikombola, ikabhe mmanganya ntendanje ya mmbone nkali tubhoneshe mbuti tushilepela.  
\v 8 Pabha tukatenda shoshowe sha tauka ya kweli, ikabhe tunapunda shumiya ya kweli.  
\v 9 Tunakwiinonyela mmanganya punkukolanga mashili nkali uwe tukakole mashili, kwa nneyo tunakunnjujilanga nkamilikanje.  
\v 10 Ligongo lya kunnjandishilanga jene bhaluwa jino nili kwatalika, ni nkupinga pushing'ishe kungwenunji nnandendanje ngalipe kwa mashili gubhambele Bhakulungwa, elo, mashili ga kuntaganga ntima na nngabha ga kummulaganga ntima. 
\s1 Shalamu ya Kumpelo 
\p  
\v 11 Kwa nneyo, ashaalongo ajangunji, nne mwanja! Nkamulanje malajilo gangu, na ntumbililanje kwiishimilika, na ntagane ntima, nkolanje ng'aniyo imo, na ntamangane kwa ulele, na a Nnungu bhakumpinganga na bha ulele, bhabhe na mmanganyanji.  
\v 12 Nnamushilananje kwa shalamu ja ukonjelo. 
\p  
\v 13 Bhandunji bhowe bha a Nnungu bhanakunnamushilanga kwa nema ja a Yeshu Kilishitu.  
\v 14 Nema ja Bhakulungwa a Yeshu Kilishitu, na kupinga kwa a Nnungu na kulundana naka Mbumu jwa Ukonjelo, ibhe na mmanganyanji mmowe.